overview: The ultimate action-adventure saga with Superstar Steve Hammond, Falcon idol Mark Baxter, Dcota, Karl Thomas, Lee Jennings, Josh Taylor, Matt Clarke & huge Greg Conrad. This FalconPac video opens up as a funny spoof of the popular 1960's television show, Mission Impossible. Great Falcon sex-parody with a tongue-in-cheek storyline chock full of hairless, well-defined men with thick, long dicks and plenty of position variety.
title: Mission Accomplished
